datalog_actions: can_access(S, O) :- Subject(S), Object(O), (has_permission(S, "permission:mli:vi-operations"); has_permission(S, "permission:mli:vi-request-operations"); has_permission(S, "permission:mli:replanning:vr-it-operations"); has_permission(S, "permission:mli:replanning:vlink-operations"); has_permission(S, "permission:sli:operations")).
